{"article_id":"coDkQeSrJTlE3OEv","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"House Republicans postponed taking up the American Health Care Act","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"after it became clear that it did not have the votes","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"to pass .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"BREAKING :","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"AP Source :","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"House GOP leaders delay vote on health care repeal bill , in setback for President Trump and Speaker Ryan .","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"- The Associated Press","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"( @ AP )","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"March 23 , 2017","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"# BREAKING :","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"House leaders have canceled a planned Thursday night vote on a GOP plan","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"to repeal","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"and replace Obamacare","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"https : //t.co/Yg9p34KSPT","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"pic.twitter.com/jq8NdJAtrB","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"- POLITICO","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"( @ politico )","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"March 23 , 2017","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"Fox News ' Shepard Smith said","depth":4},{"id":19,"text":"that a closed door meeting is going to be held around 7 P.M. EST .","depth":4},{"id":20,"text":"The bill had a rocky start from the beginning ,","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"with Medicaid expansion being left intact in the Obamacare replacement legislation .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"That seemed to poison the well with House conservatives .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"Yet , go too far on tweaking Medicaid ,","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"and then the moderate Republican lawmakers would bolt .","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"When the Congressional Budget Office gave the bill a less than stellar report card ,","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"moderates began to break away .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"Fox News ' Chad Pergram elaborated on","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"this seesaw balancing act between the House Republican leadership , members of the moderate Tuesday Group ,","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"which number around 50 members ,","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"and the conservative House Freedom Caucus .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"In short , the votes were not there today .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"The House GOP could only afford to lose 21 members .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"By Thursday afternoon , 30-40 members were in the \" no \" column","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"( via WaPo ) :","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"As of midafternoon Thursday , 37 House Republicans","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"- mainly Freedom Caucus members -","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"had announced their opposition to the bill ,","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"known as the American Health Care Act .","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"Trump will also meet Thursday with members of the moderate \" Tuesday Group , \"","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"Spicer said .","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"On Wednesday , four Republican moderates","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"- Reps. Charlie Dent","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"( Pa. ) ,","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"Frank A. LoBiondo","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"( N.J. ) ,","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"Daniel Donovan","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"( N.Y. )","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"and David Young","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"( Iowa ) -","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"announced their opposition ,","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"increasing pressure on leaders","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"to win over conservatives .","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"GOP leaders appeared to be making some headway","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"in bringing the measure to the floor for a vote Thursday .","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"The price","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"for doing so , however , may be striking popular provisions in former president Barack Obama ' s Affordable Care Act","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"that could make it even more difficult to pass legislation in the Senate .","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"This high-wire balancing act ,","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"in which Republicans are catering to conservatives in the House with the knowledge","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"that they still must woo moderates","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"to get legislation to Trump ' s desk ,","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"could not only reshape the nation ' s health-care system","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"but could also have uncertain electoral repercussions for the new majority .","depth":5},{"id":64,"text":"Yet , even with these House obstacles to the bill .","depth":5},{"id":65,"text":"The Senate has signaled","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"that the support","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"to pass it","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"isn ' t there .","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"Sen. Tom Cotton","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"( R-AR )","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"said this ,","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"warning his House colleagues to not support a bill","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"that doesn ' t have a chance in the Senate .","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"As Guy mentioned before ,","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"asking for more time is not really an option","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"since Republicans have had several years","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"to get their replacement plan together .","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"The base would not tolerate a delay on an issue of this magnitude .","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"Rep. Mark Meadows :","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"\" We have not gotten enough of our members","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"to get to yes at this point \" on the health care bill","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"https : //t.co/g93RHXQhX","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"9 - CNN Politics","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"( @ CNNPolitics )","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"March 23 , 2017","depth":6},{"id":86,"text":"Outside of his office , chair of the House Freedom Caucus Rep. Mark Meadows","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"( R-NC )","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"said","depth":6},{"id":89,"text":"that progress was being made , especially on the issue","depth":6},{"id":90,"text":"of reducing premiums from coast to coast .","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"He did confirm","depth":5},{"id":92,"text":"that there is engagement with president on this bill ,","depth":6},{"id":93,"text":"and that he ' s had discussions with his Senate colleagues .","depth":6},{"id":94,"text":"Meadows is optimistic","depth":5},{"id":95,"text":"that common ground can be found for 51 or 52 senators to get behind this legislation .","depth":5},{"id":96,"text":"The congressman did not get into specifics .","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"What he did say","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"was that this whole legislative debate is not about what he wants ,","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"but what our constituents back home have demanded for the past several years","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"concerning health care reform .","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"\" We ' re going to get to the finish line , \"","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"he said confidently .","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"Meadows also said","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"that he would welcome Democratic support ,","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"but we 're not there yet .","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"He also said","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"that Speaker Paul Ryan is working hard","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"to get this done ,","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"noting","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"that there are a number of negotiations","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"going on","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"as we speak .","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"The goal is to find a consensus","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"and try to get the 30-40 \" no \" votes into the \" yes \" column .","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"Right now , Mr. Meadows is still a `` no '' vote .","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"Rep. Mark Meadows :","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"\" I am still a no at this time .","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"I am desperately trying to get to yes \"","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"ht